videos.headline: So. Mississippi strip-sacks QB, recovers ball in end zone for TD
videos.description: Southern Mississippi strip-sacks QB Jack Abraham and recovers his ball in the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: UL Monroe WR burns DBs for 49-yard TD
videos.description: UL Monroe WR Marcus Green toasts defenders for a 49-yard touchdown, giving them the lead.

videos.headline: UL Monroe's late INT ends Southern Mississippi comeback bid
videos.description: UL Monroe's Cortez Sisco Jr. intercepts Jack Abraham's pass with 22 seconds left to hold on for win 21-20.
